*  CSCI 5239  - Schreuder Advanced Computer Graphics
* Dwight Browne
* Final project   DRAGONFLY SCREEN SAVER II   
* Key Bindings:
* Arrows change view angle
* ESC Exit
* home_key or h:  set Azimuth and elevation to 0.
* w move camera forward.
* a move camera left.
* s move camera back.
* d move camera right.


Keypress
* o:  Polygon mode
* SPACE stop Light animation.
* , to decrease rotation speed
* . to increase rotation speed
* g stop motion
* h stop background
* n increase Z of light
* m decrease Z of light
* y wing movement
* b increase smoke density
* v decrease smoke density
* P perspective
* t texture



TO RUN
* run final

Total time 70 hours 

ISSUES:
had to abandon original "New framework" and focused on shaders

FEATURES:
Procedural shaders
